data.description: Welcome Home! This 4 bedrooms, 2 bathroom home has n exterior paint, new carpet, new fence, newer roof (2017), updated bathroom and did we mention IN-GROUND POOL with covered patio off the back? Offering a 1% Rate Buy Down with acceptable offer! Come relax in the completely private backyard by the pool or BBQ on the patio. Large basement with living room, legal bedroom and bathroom. This home is a short distance from Dwight Merkel Park, close to downtown Spokane and Riverside State Park. Situated in a quiet cul-de-sac off a quiet street. New front load washer/dryer with pedestals are included in sale of the home. Check out this home today!
